{
  "stem": "24268.4",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He had two choices-- or I should live or my baby-- the baby.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So Moris says, I want them both alive.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "If not, you're gonna be dead.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the whole camp, wherever they live in Germany, in the camp, Deggendorf-- one lady, my neighbor, which I got a letter, she was a very dear person to me.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I needed a momma.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] So she was about 36.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She was beautiful people.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I still have it, and she wrote it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I think she lived in-- in Montreal.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I got a beautiful letter from her.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So she passed out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Everybody else was crying.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And now they still live here a man who remember that.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "All the camp, everybody was on bicycles in front of the hospital.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they say if there [LAUGHS] gonna something happen, they were gonna kill.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there was-- they still remember this.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he, sure enough, he got scared.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then two doctors, I recall, and they-- he said the last minute, I think he put some anesthetic.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he screamed at me he wanted a live child.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "That's what he shouted at me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He wanted a live child.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I couldn't take it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I just passed out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And sure enough, she-- and they woke me-- say, you see, the beautiful [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "This means the beautiful baby.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And that was my daughter, and everybody loved her.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "She was everybody's baby.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "My-- my-- a friend of mine who she's in Israel, she said that the kids were jealous of her, because all that she should talk was about Rita and even having her own.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And she was so-- was a-- they been wonderful people.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
